پروانه‌ی اختصاصی پنل Aras-GP
Version 1.0

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
SCOPE / دامنه‌ی شمول
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This licence governs ONLY the contents of the `panel/` directory (the
"Panel"): its Python modules, HTML templates, CSS, JavaScript, and the
Aras-GP brand assets under `panel/static/brand/`.

It does NOT apply to the relay engine. The files under `src/`, `deploy/`,
`main.py` and `setup.py` — including `src/account_manager.py` and the
modifications made to `src/proxy_server.py` for per-user authentication —
remain under the MIT licence stated in the repository root `LICENSE` file,
because they are derived from MIT-licensed code. Nothing in this document
attempts to revoke or narrow that grant.

این پروانه فقط شامل محتویات پوشه‌ی `panel/` است. موتور رله زیر `src/` و
`deploy/` همچنان تحت پروانه‌ی MIT مندرج در فایل `LICENSE` ریشه‌ی مخزن باقی
می‌ماند.

