1. GRANT / اعطای حق استفاده
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Subject to the restrictions below, the copyright holder grants you a
non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable licence to:

  (a) install and run the Panel for your own personal or internal
      organisational use;
  (b) modify the Panel's source for that same use;
  (c) inspect, audit, and security-test any part of the Panel.

Right (c) is granted unconditionally and may not be waived. The Panel ships
unobfuscated on purpose: software used to circumvent censorship must be
auditable by the people whose safety depends on it.

