2. RESTRICTIONS / محدودیت‌ها
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Without prior WRITTEN permission from the copyright holder, you may NOT:

  2.1  Remove, replace, obscure, or alter the Aras-GP branding — including
       the name "Aras-GP", the SVG mark in `panel/static/brand/`, the
       wordmark, the colour system, or the attribution in the footer — in
       any copy you distribute or make available to a third party.

  2.2  Rebrand the Panel, or present it (in whole or in substantial part)
       under a different product name or identity.

  2.3  Sell, resell, sublicense, rent, lease, or otherwise commercially
       distribute the Panel or any derivative of it, whether standalone,
       bundled, or as part of a hosted service offered to third parties.

  2.4  Redistribute the Panel publicly (including uploading it to a public
       repository, marketplace, or file-sharing service) in modified form.

  2.5  Remove or weaken the security controls in Section 4, or the
       disclaimer displayed in the Panel's footer.

بدون اجازه‌ی کتبی، حذف یا تغییر برندینگ، ری‌برندسازی، و فروش مجدد ممنوع است.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. PERMITTED WITHOUT PERMISSION / موارد مجاز بدون اجازه
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

For clarity, the following are always permitted:

  3.1  Running an unlimited number of private instances for yourself, your
       family, or your organisation's own users.

  3.2  Publishing security research, vulnerability reports, or code review
       of the Panel, including quoting the source as needed.

  3.3  Sharing unmodified copies privately with individuals, provided the
       branding and this licence file travel with them.

  3.4  Charging your own end users for a proxy service you operate using
       the Panel — the restriction in 2.3 covers selling the software, not
       operating it.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. SECURITY AND PRIVACY COVENANTS / تعهدات امنیتی
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

The copyright holder commits, for as long as this licence is in force, that
the Panel will NOT contain:

  4.1  any telemetry, analytics, beacon, or phone-home mechanism that
       transmits user identity, IP addresses, traffic statistics, or
       configuration to the copyright holder or any third party;

  4.2  any remote kill switch, remote disablement, or remote configuration
       channel affecting a user's installation;

  4.3  any obfuscated, packed, or deliberately unreadable code that would
       impede independent security auditing;

  4.4  any licence-enforcement mechanism requiring network contact. The
       optional licence gate in `panel/licensing.py` verifies an Ed25519
       signature entirely offline and makes no network request of any kind.

These are commitments of the licensor to the licensee, not restrictions on
the licensee. If any future version of the Panel violates them, that version
is not covered by this licence.

این تعهدات به این دلیل وجود دارند که این ابزار برای عبور از سانسور و نظارت
ساخته شده است؛ هر سازوکار پنهانِ ارتباط با یک سرور مرکزی، دقیقاً همان خطری را
ایجاد می‌کند که این پروژه قرار است از آن محافظت کند.

